# 1. Product Vision

## Feature name

**Fixeth Career Match Engine**

## One-line pitch

Fixeth continuously scans Bangladeshi job postings, extracts role and skill demand, maps those requirements to Fixeth courses/concepts, and shows each learner which jobs they are nearly ready for after completing a course or track.

## Why this is disruptive

Most LMS platforms stop at:

- course completion,
- certificate generation,
- generic career advice.

Fixeth can go further:

- real job market data,
- Bengali-first explanation,
- skill-gap reasoning,
- course-to-job alignment,
- personalized employability signals.

The innovation is not “job scraping” alone. The innovation is:

> **A live labor-market feedback loop inside an adaptive LMS.**

The market tells Fixeth what skills are rising. Fixeth tells learners what to learn. Learners complete courses. Fixeth tells them which jobs they can confidently apply to.

