## 5.9 Add learner skill profile

Learner matching should not only depend on course completion. It should use mastery.

```sql
learner_skills (
  user_id uuid references users(id),
  skill_id uuid references skills(id),
  proficiency numeric,                  -- 0 to 100
  evidence_source text,                 -- lesson_complete, quiz, assessment, manual
  evidence_ref uuid,
  updated_at timestamptz default now(),
  primary key (user_id, skill_id)
)
```

How proficiency is calculated:

- lesson completion gives base score,
- quiz results increase confidence,
- project/assessment results give job-ready confidence,
- concept mastery can map to skill proficiency.

Example:

| Evidence | Proficiency impact |
|---|---:|
| Watched lesson | +20 |
| Completed lesson | +40 |
| Passed quiz | +20 |
| Passed project | +30 |
| Repeated incorrect quiz | -10 confidence |

