# 19. MVP vs Scalable Version

## Competition MVP

Ship:

- scraper,
- `job_market_signals`,
- trending skills API,
- dashboard/tools UI,
- seeded fallback.

Do not overbuild.

## Scalable post-MVP

Add:

- canonical skills,
- raw job posts,
- role taxonomy,
- course-to-skill map,
- learner skill profile,
- cached job matches,
- career agent explanations.

This avoids building a brittle prototype while still giving a clear path to a real product.

